OL,24,ANext Page BNW Eng NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,367,360,120,260,000,100
PN,36602
SC,0002
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F366A1782915513
OL,3,CMPs warn plans to boost rail
OL,4,Cconnections face 'clear risk' of going
OL,5,Cover budget
OL,7,FIn a report published by the
OL,8,Fcommittee, MPs compared the approach
OL,9,Fto Northern Powerhouse Rail (NPR) with
OL,10,Fthe early stages of HS2 to examine if
OL,11,Fany mistakes were being repeated.
OL,13,FNPR was first proposed in 2014 and was
OL,14,Foriginally envisioned as a new line
OL,15,Fbetween Liverpool and Hull.
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G2/9
OL,2,W/*%+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNW Eng NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,367,360,120,260,000,100
PN,36603
SC,0003
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F366A1782915513
OL,3,CMPs warn plans to boost rail
OL,4,Cconnections face 'clear risk' of going
OL,5,Cover budget
OL,7,FThe Government announced in January
OL,8,F2026 that the scheme would be
OL,9,Fdelivered in three stages, with a
OL,10,Ffunding cap of #45 billion, which
OL,11,Fcould be topped up by local
OL,12,Fcontributions.
OL,14,FThe first phase of the programme
OL,15,Finvolves improved connections on
OL,16,Fexisting lines on these routes:
OL,17,Fbetween Sheffield and Leeds; between
OL,18,FLeeds and York; and between Leeds and
OL,19,FBradford.
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G3/9
OL,2,W/*%+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNW Eng NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,367,360,120,260,000,100
PN,36604
SC,0004
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F366A1782915513
OL,3,CMPs warn plans to boost rail
OL,4,Cconnections face 'clear risk' of going
OL,5,Cover budget
OL,7,FThe PAC noted that despite 12 years of
OL,8,Fplanning, NPR "remains at an early
OL,9,Fstage".
OL,11,FIt went on: "There is considerable
OL,12,Funcertainty over scope, how the
OL,13,Fprogramme fits with other local and
OL,14,Fnational transport plans and needs,
OL,15,Fand how the department will manage and
OL,16,Fdeliver the rail improvements in
OL,17,Fpractice.
OL,26,@pD@OOUsD@MOU
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G4/9
OL,2,W/*%+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNW Eng NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,367,360,120,260,000,100
PN,36605
SC,0005
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F366A1782915513
OL,3,CMPs warn plans to boost rail
OL,4,Cconnections face 'clear risk' of going
OL,5,Cover budget
OL,7,F"There is a clear risk that the
OL,8,Fdepartment cannot deliver the full
OL,9,Fprogramme and benefits within its #45
OL,10,Fbillion funding cap."
OL,12,FThe report expressed concern that NPR
OL,13,F"may face cost pressures from planning
OL,14,Fand biodiversity requirements", and
OL,15,Fraised doubts over whether it will be
OL,16,Fable to avoid "expensive measures"
OL,17,Fsuch as "HS2's costly bat tunnel".
OL,26,@oD@AOUrD@UO]uD@AOUvD@^O]xD@OOUxD@bO]yD@
OL,26,AIOUyD@aO]
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G5/9
OL,2,W/*%+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNW Eng NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,367,360,120,260,000,100
PN,36606
SC,0006
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F366A1782915513
OL,3,CMPs warn plans to boost rail
OL,4,Cconnections face 'clear risk' of going
OL,5,Cover budget
OL,7,FHS2 Ltd built a bat protection tunnel
OL,8,Fin Buckinghamshire costing more than
OL,9,F#100 million as part of efforts to
OL,10,Fmitigate the high-speed railway's
OL,11,Fenvironmental impacts.
OL,13,FLabour MP Clive Betts, deputy chairman
OL,14,Fof the PAC, said: "The Government's
OL,15,Fgrowth strategy earlier this year
OL,16,Fsignalled that there is still an
OL,17,Fappetite to finally deliver the
OL,18,Ftransport infrastructure the North so
OL,19,Fbadly needs.
OL,26,@vD@SOU
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G6/9
OL,2,W/*%+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNW Eng NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,367,360,120,260,000,100
PN,36607
SC,0007
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F366A1782915513
OL,3,CMPs warn plans to boost rail
OL,4,Cconnections face 'clear risk' of going
OL,5,Cover budget
OL,7,F"But the spectre of HS2 hangs over
OL,8,FNorthern Powerhouse Rail.
OL,10,F"Our committee has heard troubling
OL,11,Fechoes of the same mistakes in loose
OL,12,Fgovernance that HS2 made early on, and
OL,13,Fso much of the project remains almost
OL,14,Fimpressionistic, 12 years on."
OL,16,FHe added that the decision to use
OL,17,Frepresentatives from HS2 to develop
OL,18,FNPR "does not fill us with confidence"
OL,19,Fas the former "has been a casebook
OL,20,Fexample of how not to run a major
OL,21,Fproject".
OL,26,@oD@AOUrD@AOUvD@^O]zD@EOUzD@fO]{D@OOU}D@
OL,26,AHO]
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G7/9
OL,2,W/*%+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
