PN,36608
SC,0008
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F366A1782915513
OL,3,CMPs warn plans to boost rail
OL,4,Cconnections face 'clear risk' of going
OL,5,Cover budget
OL,7,FA Department for Transport
OL,8,Fspokesperson said: "NPR will not
OL,9,Frepeat the mistakes of HS2 which is
OL,10,Fwhy we accepted all the
OL,11,Frecommendations of the James Stewart
OL,12,FReview and are taking a disciplined,
OL,13,Fphased approach, completing detailed
OL,14,Ftechnical work with all stakeholders
OL,15,Fbefore fixing precise choices for
OL,16,Fmajor infrastructure.
OL,18,F"Since announcing NPR in January, we
OL,19,Fhave worked closely with Mayors to
OL,20,Ftake the project forward.
OL,26,@pD@TOUzD@AOU
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G8/9
